{"tid":1720873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旭日行動要贏，一定要爭取被罷工唔扣假","createTime":"2019-11-14T13:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:00.000Z","uid":272805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3c8efd974fc6e6d3c7b6ad543e4e20850fa19a","tid":1720873,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"大家都知香港人有幾鍾意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其中一個原因係唔返工會<span style=\"color: red;\">俾人扣大假</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果唔使扣假呢？<br />\n咁最大嘅返工誘因就已經消失左（個個都返工，唔通個個都想返工咩）<br />\n<br />\n方法<br />\n1. Email 俾各大公司/NGO ，因為路面情況，有可能返唔到工，唔好因為咁樣而懲罰員工，或者扣假，僱主亦應該保障員工安全，留係安全嘅地方bababa<br />\n<br />\n2.搵深黃公司帶頭（100毛之類），然後鼓勵人跟從，造成羊群效應<br />\n<br />\n做得成嘅話，真係攞正牌擺工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得OK嘅，麻煩推一推俾更多人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人報仇！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e9b773c2fd019176110558426e1e12a9fc7202f","tid":1720873,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8669d9c6e557affa75b876e54242249a4bde6b69","tid":1720873,"uid":127395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3efaec051c37555c45685923c0a5afac0dfdc1d","tid":1720873,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"無晒行動post<br />\n今日太遲行動喇"}]}